1. Install the modified versions of GMP and MPFR
	See the HOWTO files in the directories for GMP and MPFR.

2. Download Valgrind
	http://valgrind.org/downloads/current.html
	FpDebug was tested with a nightly version of Valgrind 3.7 (now final).

2. Add FpDebug to Valgrind:
	Edit Makefile.am by adding the new directory fpdebug to the EXP_TOOLS variables.
	Edit configure.in by adding fpdebug/Makefile to the AC_CONFIG_FILES list.

3. Build Valgrind:
	Read the README file in the main Valgrind directory.

To test if everything works (optional):

4. Compile one of the examples
	See the README file in fpdebug/examples.	

5. Use FpDebug for analyzing the example
	valgrind --tool=fpdebug filename


General structure of using Valgrind with FpDebug:
	valgrind [valgrind options]--tool=fpdebug [fpdebug options] clientprogram [client options]

Example:
	valgrind --trace-children=yes --tool=fpdebug --precision=128 /glpk-4.47/examples/glpsol --math problem.mod

